seeing all of these Spotify ‘your artist of the decade’ pictures made me emotional. It’s hard to fully know the reach you’re having with the music you create, and these things struck my soul.. perhaps the highest compliment possible. Flattered and humbled. love you all ❤️
Very excited to announce @nealbrennan joining me for the LA solo piano shows and @joshjohnsoncomedy in NY! A few tickets for LA are still available, follow the link in bio.

I have so much love and respect for this man. A friend who has been so generous in including me and giving me confidence in this industry. It’s been amazing to watch him take over the world with a sound he created. I was relieved to see him sat next to me at the Dior Men’s show.
